[-10, 50, 120, 75, 100, -5, 25] >> values.

"--- Removing Outliers ---" >> Display.

values >> Filter:
    @ >> check:
        is < 0: false >> Return.
        is > 100: false >> Return.
    ..
    true >> Return.
.. >> valid_values.

"Valid values: " >> msg.
(valid_values >> ToJson) >+> msg.
msg >> Display.
